INSERT INTO `crp_indicator_reports` (`id`,`target`,`next_target`,`actual`,`support_links`,`deviation`,`liaison_institution_id`,`indicator_id`,`year`,`last_update`,`acronym`) VALUES (1032,'4',NULL,'5','1) CSA-Plan: \r\n- Presentation made at the CSA Global conference in Montpellier: http://www.slideshare.net/cgiarclimate/l21-csa-conference-campbell-et-al-csa-plan-316final?qid=9cc2cdc2-c0ad-41f3-9c60-d21167010e31&v=qf1&b=&from_search=24\r\n- Poster: https://www.dropbox.com/s/0een0fnqjo6eqlk/CSA-Plan%20Poster1.pdf?dl=0 \r\n- Video on the Prioritization framework: https://www.powtoon.com/show/b0JHzjnt6LT/csa-prioritization-framework/#/\r\n- Guidebook Participatory Process under developement\r\n- Blog post: Prioritization pilot in Mali: http://ccafs.cgiar.org/blog/climate-smart-solutions-mali#.VSMFp5OxjLk\r\n- Blog post:  Creating a \'learning center\' for agricultural development in Guatemala: http://ccafs.cgiar.org/blog/creating-learning-center-agricultural-development-guatemala#.VSMF_ZOxjLk\r\n\r\n\r\n2) Country profiles in LAC with WorldBank : Profiles for 7 countries were jointly produced with the CIAT team and presented to the Worldbank and external audiences during 2014.  \r\n- See more at: http://www.ciatnews.cgiar.org/2014/10/30/country-profiles-on-climate-smart-agriculture-well-received-at-the-world-bank/#sthash.0AxqfKl5.dpuf\r\n- http://dapa.ciat.cgiar.org/csa-profiles/\r\n- http://ccafs.cgiar.org/research-highlight/new-latin-america-country-profiles-open-pathways-reaching- climate-smart#.VOdaofmG9LE\r\n- http://ciatblogs.cgiar.org/support/world-bank-smart-investments-in-triple-win-agriculture/\r\n- http://climate-l.iisd.org/news/ciat-catie-produce-lac-climate-smart-agriculture-profiles/ \r\n\r\n3) Climate Analogue Tool:  http://www.ccafs-analogues.org/tool/ \r\n- Climate Analogues Tool explanatory video:  https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=f9C1RpV6ta0\r\n- Blog posts: \r\n•Climate scenarios and analogues: A glimpse into past, present and future climates.\r\nhttp